INSERT INTO contacts (
  propertyId, name, relationship, phone1, address,
  createdAt, updatedAt
) VALUES (
  (SELECT id FROM properties WHERE addressLine1 = '4700 SW 18th St' AND city = 'West Park' ORDER BY id DESC LIMIT 1),
  'Devin Johnson',
  'Owner',
  '(954) 923-0155',
  '4700 SW 18th St, West Park, FL 33023',
  NOW(),
  NOW()
);
